# English-First Translation Rule

Use `no-visible-source-text-i18n.mdc` as the canonical UI text rule.

- Define and maintain product text in English first (keys + English defaults).
- Add German as a separate translation layer, never by replacing English source text.
- Keep i18n non-intrusive: use a shared translation helper/provider instead of scattered locale conditionals.
- Keep translation config in `frontend/src/i18n/translations.json`.
- For new UI text: add English key/default first, then add or adjust translation JSON.
